{"tid":1816274,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(通輯犯) 藏冰毒休班警違感化令沒到庭　官發拘捕令","createTime":"2020-01-08T06:23:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-08T11:49:34.000Z","uid":184679,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"3373abba13a7e2aa5de9264df21f295d9e239cf2","tid":1816274,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T06:23:47.000Z","msg":"休班警員去年4月經羅湖返港，遭海關截停時揭發藏有0.09克冰毒、一粒俗稱「偉哥」的含昔多芬藥丸和238支未完稅香煙。他早前承認各一項未根據並按照入口許可證的規定輸入禁運物品、藏毒、藏有應課稅品和未有向海關人員申報罪，上月被判感化令。惟被告涉以「共用餐具唔夠文明」等為由拒絕入住戒毒所，被指違反感化官指示，今日（8日）原上庭解釋，卻缺席聆訊，裁判官遂發出拘捕令。<br />\n<br />\n報稱警員的被告馬道宸（46歲），今早沒有在粉嶺裁判法院出庭。署理主任裁判官蘇文隆指出，根據進度報告，被告違反感化官的指示及建議。蘇官遂頒下拘捕令，下令緝拿被告歸案後不准保釋。<br />\n<br />\n被告去年4月經羅湖管制站返港，途經入境大堂遭截停，在身上及行李被搜出涉案物品，他上庭承認控罪。同年12月，他被判感化18個月及罰款5000元，其間須聽從感化官指示，包括入住戒毒機構晨曦會。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，被告上月入住戒毒所時，不滿吃飯要與他人共用餐具，認為「唔夠文明」，又投訴社工沒有為他申請傷殘津貼，因此離開戒毒所。被告亦聲稱想申請上訴，多番拒絕與感化官聯絡；至上月相約與感化官商討進度報告，最後缺席會面。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200108/s00001/1578460460681/%E8%97%8F%E5%86%B0%E6%AF%92%E4%BC%91%E7%8F%AD%E8%AD%A6%E9%81%95%E6%84%9F%E5%8C%96%E4%BB%A4%E6%B2%92%E5%88%B0%E5%BA%AD-%E5%AE%98%E7%99%BC%E6%8B%98%E6%8D%95%E4%BB%A4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200108%2Fs00001%2F1578460460681%2F%25E8%2597%258F%25E5%2586%25B0%25E6%25AF%2592%25E4%25BC%2591%25E7%258F%25AD%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%2581%2595%25E6%2584%259F%25E5%258C%2596%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E6%25B2%2592%25E5%2588%25B0%25E5%25BA%25AD-%25E5%25AE%2598%25E7%2599%25BC%25E6%258B%2598%25E6%258D%2595%25E4%25BB%25A4&d=dJWoD07mVvvIIonm04m6Imipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=bcb0cdd4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200108%2Fs00001%2F1578460460681%2F%25E8%2597%258F%25E5%2586%25B0%25E6%25AF%2592%25E4%25BC%2591%25E7%258F%25AD%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%2581%2595%25E6%2584%259F%25E5%258C%2596%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E6%25B2%2592%25E5%2588%25B0%25E5%25BA%25AD-%25E5%25AE%2598%25E7%2599%25BC%25E6%258B%2598%25E6%258D%2595%25E4%25BB%25A4&h=88fe1483\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200108/s00001/1578460460681/%E8%97%8F%E5%86%B0%E6%AF%92%E4%BC%91%E7%8F%AD%E8%AD%A6%E9%81%95%E6%84%9F%E5%8C%96%E4%BB%A4%E6%B2%92%E5%88%B0%E5%BA%AD-%E5%AE%98%E7%99%BC%E6%8B%98%E6%8D%95%E4%BB%A4</a>"},{"pid":"33e4f723a377ed0db32ad44fa49a4d7cd8470f8e","tid":1816274,"uid":38523,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T06:24:39.000Z","msg":"其實入面有冇一個係正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21c0933f2c04d86097042ad1ba5a8091cd25f7ba","tid":1816274,"uid":45841,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T06:24:48.000Z","msg":"全港最大犯罪集團<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c17969d0b9f2b9dd3e09c15068c927871e162e1","tid":1816274,"uid":290883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T06:27:32.000Z","msg":"魔警！！"},{"pid":"b3e16445796c1c682e14f9219e1b9cdf73b4d74e","tid":1816274,"uid":96648,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T06:40:00.000Z","msg":"藍蛆點睇"},{"pid":"b89c03719b5e2c0ca41bb9934bbeb7bfc7a2fc23","tid":1816274,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T07:41:28.000Z","msg":"係時候做啲野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66878367a51e8a0556c224c74c3bd61c69058140","tid":1816274,"uid":329698,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T07:42:36.000Z","msg":"係咪搵黑警拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f67ce065b33767ac85cec24a87fff7b59a4061d","tid":1816274,"uid":124711,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T07:43:23.000Z","msg":"三萬隻畜牲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img